description:
Undertaker has long, grey hair with a few braids throughout, which is worn so as to hide his eyes. He has a noticeable scar across his face, although how he acquired it is unknown, and has long, black fingernails. He also wears all black, including an incredibly long, black top hat, and a he wears a long, grey scarf across his chest, with it knotted by his hips.
Source: kuroshitsuji.wikia.com
name: Undertaker
